text: Edward king gret Edwine abbot & Alfgæt scirrefa freondlice.
& ic ciþe eow þat ic habbe gegifan Teinfriþe mine circwirhtan þæt land æt Scepertune mid sace & mid socne, scotfreo & gafulfreo on hundred & on scire.
& ic nelle geþafian þæt him ani man mid anigne þinga misbeode ac habbe he infangeneþeof & flimene frimþe.
